<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent } from 'vue'
import { Geo } from '../classes/Geo'
import CiWall1 from '@/components/CiWall1.vue'
import CiWeather1 from '@/components/CiWeather1.vue'
import CiPump1 from '@/components/CiPump1.vue'
// import CiSocket2 from '@/components/CiSocket2.vue'
// import CiDoor from '@/components/CiDoor.vue'
// import CiLamp from '@/components/CiLamp.vue'
// import CiMotion from '@/components/CiMotion.vue'

export default defineComponent({
  name: 'Erdgeschoss',
  components: {
    CiWall1,
    CiWeather1,
    CiPump1
    // CiSocket2
    // CiDoor,
    // CiLamp,
    // CiMotion
  },
  computed: {
    geo: function (): Geo {
      const geo1 = new Geo(0, 0)
      return geo1
    },
    dx: function (): number { return (this.geo.dxo()) },
    dy: function (): number { return (this.geo.dyo()) }
  },
  methods: {
    showErdgeschoss: function () {
      console.log('CLICK - showErdgeschoss', '')
      return this.$router.push({ name: 'Erdgeschoss' })
    }
  }
})
</script>

<style scoped>
 .styleStiege { font: bold 60px sans-serif; fill: red; cursor: pointer; }

 #e2su {
   cursor: pointer;
 }
</style>
